461
00:36:40,330 --> 00:36:41,976
Don't do anything shameful.

462
00:36:43,270 --> 00:36:44,575
Stop here.

463
00:36:49,870 --> 00:36:51,586
You need to know how it feels.

464
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:56,411
To have aged...

465
00:36:56,411 --> 00:36:59,095
